fj-dispatch batched-operand gather direct-path candidate golden

source tests:
- batching::tests::test_batch_trace_gather_batched_operand_shared_indices
- batching::tests::test_batch_trace_gather_batched_operand_shared_indices_rank3_partial_slice
- batching::tests::test_batch_trace_gather_batched_operand_batched_indices
